FBIS4-63087 "drsov098_o_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-098 Daily Report 19 May 1994 Uzbekistan EU Program for Energy Saving, Power Engineering Outlined EU Program for Energy Saving, Power Engineering Outlined LD1905170294 Tashkent UZBEKISTAN APN in Russian 0945 GMT 19 May 94 LD1905170294 Tashkent UZBEKISTAN APN Russian BFN [Text] Today the presentation of the European Union's program on the development of power engineering and energy saving was held in Tashkent. This program consists of four large projects which covers all the areas in industry. The implementation of these projects will make it possible to save about 250 million kilowatt hours of energy annually. The European Union has allocated $7 million for this project. The program is already operating and in the first quarter of this year 218,000 tonnes of fuel units have been saved.
